{
  "_comment": "Experimental example only. The current Windows environment has not established reliable production command-hook execution; do not deploy this automatically. Verified against Claude Code v2.1.50 project-local hooks UI on 2026-07-01. Use matcher-group structure, not the older flat event handler shape.",
  "_release_path_template": "{install_dir}\\taskbar_widget_hook.exe",
